description: Try our easy to follow Sweet Potato Fries recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Chips & fries,Pescatarian,Low saturated fat,Seafood free,Low salt,Gluten free,Tree nut free,Egg free,Sesame free,Halal,High fibre,Soy free,Wheat free,Vegetarian,Sweet potato,Vegan,Dairy free,Peanut free
name: Sweet Potato Fries Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Peel sweet potatoes. Trim ends and cut into thick chips. Toss in a bowl with oil to coat. Season with salt and pepper. Arrange in a single layer on a large oven tray lined with baking paper. Bake for 25 minutes or until tender and golden.
